# RPC endpoint URL for the GenLayer network.
# Defaults to studionet (https://studio.genlayer.com/api) when unset.
# Override for localnet (http://localhost:4000/api) or testnets.
RPC_URL=https://studio.genlayer.com/api

# Optional. Leave commented to use an ephemeral account.
# - Studio (default): ephemeral is fine — Studio is gasless.
# - Testnets / localnet with persistent state: set a funded 0x-prefixed key.
# PRIVATE_KEY=0x...
